Seoul Experience Football Theme Museum is a composite football theme park with football as the theme and integrating IT technology. You can experience VR technology, experience the fun of kicking, passing, shooting and defending in the actual arena, and watch the World Cup. National representative uniforms and trophy displays, educational programs to learn football, photoshoots and more.

The Stamp Museum is located in Seoul, South Korea. The museum displays a wide variety of stamps. Through these exhibits, tourists can better understand the history and culture of the postal service. There is a stamp experience area in the museum. After taking pictures at the designated location, the staff will process the stamps, and then tourists can get an exclusive stamp. In addition, there is a museum souvenir shop next to the information desk.
